User Journey 
    A user visits ${siteDefinition} from an Impact tracking link
        Impact will dynamically populate a Click Id value in a landing page URL parameter called im_ref
            e.g. https://${firstSiteDefinition}?im_ref=14zqjADgl7uNcN9V8uPPgD3Cj:oube4Osd-nEHg-PBfM
        ${accountName} loads Impact’s Universal Tracking Tag in the head followed by the Identify function in the body
    User navigates around ${firstSiteDefinition}
        ${accountName} loads Impact’s Universal Tracking Tag in the head followed by the Identify function in the body on every page of the site
    User completes a/an ${eventName} event
        ${accountName} loads Impact’s Universal Tracking Tag in the head followed by the trackCoversion function in the body
